{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji29.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给刘天民的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给刘天民的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年10月19日）天民女士："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来信收到，甚谢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李耿侯已牺牲。李介侯现在北京人民革命大学学习，情况尚好，知注并闻。此复，顺致"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月十九日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]刘天民，湖南韶山市杨林乡善扶村人，郭梓材的妻子，和杨开慧关系密切。大革命时期曾从事学生运动和青年工作，后长期做教育工作。曾任湘潭市政协委员。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":10,"day":19}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":258,"page_end":258},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}